prompt.sse_detail:
DeepSeek/OpenAI 流式 SSE 格式:
``` data: {"choices":[{"delta":{"role":"assistant"},"index":0}],"created":1234567890}

 data: {"choices":[{"delta":{"content":"你好"},"index":0}],"created":1234567890}

 data: {"choices":[{"delta":{"content":"，我们"},"index":0}],"created":1234567890}

 data: {"choices":[{"delta":{"content":"开始吧"},"index":0}],"created":1234567890}

 data: [DONE]

 ```
解析逻辑: - 行是否以 "data: " 开头 → 否：跳过 - 内容是 "[DONE]" → 结束 - 解析 JSON → choices[0].delta.get("content", "") → 非空则 yield
注意: - role 字段的 delta 没有 content，跳过 - finish_reason 出现在最后一个 choice delta 中，不产出 content - 多个 choice 只取 index=0
